summary: This document contains location data related to a mobile number associated with the Epstein case, initiated by AT&T. It provides details about the confidence level of the location estimate and cautions about the accuracy of the data sourced from various databases.
keyFacts: The document was initiated on June 30, 2020.
It provides location data for a mobile number with a confidence level of 90.
The location data is sourced from AT&T's 4G-GMPC system.
The radius of the location estimate is 3339 meters.
Caution is advised in using the location data for investigative purposes due to potential inaccuracies.
